'''Heath John Davids''' (August 24th, 1939 - 2003) (1999-2003 in reality) was the alias of [[Jonathan Zeymmo]] while he was hiding in [[Papua New Guinea]]. He worked as a security guard for a local museum. After Zeymmo was caught and deported to the [[United States]], Davids' absence, despite the public being aware of the truth, was filed off as natural causes.
